metadata.name: (A)I am the only artist now
metadata.description:
A piece made for Claire Silver's 3rd AI art contest. 

A satirical take on the non-AI side's arguments that AI steals art and that AI will replace all artists.

-- 
Artwork made with AI, Photoshop and gifmaker.
Music made by AI with text2music.
MP4, 2048x2048
